snippet.title: The Dark Knight Rises - iOS/Android - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
The Dark Knight Rises is now available on the App Store and on Google Play in some territories. 
And very soon in the rest of the world. 

Play the exclusive game inspired by the movie. 

Want to know when it will be released in your country? Check out the release dates list here: http://www.gameloft.com/minisites/the-dark-knight-rises-release-date/ 

Visit our official site at http://www.gameloft.com 
Follow us on Twitter at http://glft.co/GameloftonTwitter 
Like us on Facebook at http://facebook.com/Gameloft 
Check out our videos and game trailers on http://www.youtube.com/Gameloft
Discover our blog at http://glft.co/Gameloft_Official_Blog
